GNUTLS_A_DECRYPTION_FAILED               21      Decryption failed
GNUTLS_A_RECORD_OVERFLOW                 22      Record overflow
GNUTLS_A_DECOMPRESSION_FAILURE           30      Decompression failed
GNUTLS_A_HANDSHAKE_FAILURE               40      Handshake failed
